infos.value: Wait a minute. Is this really all the barbaric Fennes has to offer?
Or did you just lose your nerve around little ole me?
I feel...th' power...welling up... Can't...hold it.
Kill...kill yer, kill. Kill... I will...never...yield.
"Never yield," you say?
Then let's see it.
I'll spill your life's blood before you even get a swing in.
Gwwwaaaaaahhh!
If you won't make a move...then allow me!
What's wrong? No fight left in you already?
Agh...!
Wh-what was that!?
I couldn't even see him, aye!
G-getting cold feet, are you? Zazan...
Rairyuu's your partner, isn't he? You should be out for revenge, aye?
Th-this man is...unbelievable.
Meaning...?
We should make a run for it!
Kill...kill yer...kill...
It seems that slaying Rairyuu has brought him back to his senses a bit.
King Muraga... To Leonis Castle...
Kill...Mont.
His Fierceness is truly terrifying.
Even if we overthrow Leonis...at this rate, what will become of Fennes?
